.
.TP
bad signed floating value (examples: 5.125, -5.125, or 5.125E05)
.
.TP
bad positive floating value (examples: 5.125 or 5.125E05)
.
.TP
bad value (0.0 to 1.0)
.
.TP
bad value (0.0 to 1.0 or 1.0E-4), and down <= same <= up
.
.TP
tkinter import messagebox
.
.TP
bad signed float value (examples: 5.125, -5.125 or 5.125E05)
.
.TP
